naan sigappu manithan ( english : i am a red man ) is a 2014 tamil psychological thriller film directed by thiru and produced by utv motion pictures . co-produced by vishal , the film stars himself in the leading role with lakshmi menon and iniya in supporting roles , while g. v. prakash kumar composed the film 's music . the film deals with &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it was released on 11 april 2014 . it is dubbed into hindi as pyaar reloaded .